{"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/registerforpushnotificationswith:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Registers the device for push notifications with initial tags.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSDictionary","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSDictionary"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"tags"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Dictionary of tag names and values to set during registration."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Supported value types: NSString, NSNumber, NSArray (for list tags)."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"tags"}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Combines push notification registration with tag assignment in a single operation."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This is more efficient than calling registerForPushNotifications and setTags separately,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as tags are sent to the server along with the registration request."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this method when you have user attributes available at the time of registration,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as during onboarding or after user authentication.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Register with user attributes after sign-up:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class SignUpCoordinator {","","    func completeSignUp(user: User, source: SignUpSource) {","        let registrationTags: [String: Any] = [","            \"user_type\": user.accountType.rawValue,","            \"signup_source\": source.analyticsValue,","            \"signup_date\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: Date()),","            \"interests\": user.selectedInterests,","            \"language\": Locale.current.languageCode ?? \"en\",","            \"app_version\": Bundle.main.appVersion","        ]","","        Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications(with: registrationTags)","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(user.id)","        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmail(user.email)","    }","}","","extension Bundle {","    var appVersion: String {","        infoDictionary?[\"CFBundleShortVersionString\"] as? String ?? \"unknown\"","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/registerForPushNotificationsWith:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"metadata":{"title":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)registerForPushNotificationsWith:","roleHeading":"Type Method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:"}]},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/registerForPushNotificationsWith:":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Registers the device for push notifications with initial tags."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/registerforpushnotificationswith:","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/registerForPushNotificationsWith:","title":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","role":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"title":"PWConfiguration","type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"PushwooshCore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}]}}}